     <p>Lots of small tasks here and there that are not tracked will add up to lost revenues. Make sure that every client call, e-mail response and meeting time gets tracked.</p>
   </div>
   <div class="landing-feature">
     <img src="photos/work-management-software-3.jpg" alt="Tracking time on a subway">
     <h2>What time management habits should I change?</h2>
     <p>Toggl reports will show you how many hours a day you are really being productive. Analizing this information gives you the opportunity to shift priorities and maximise productive time.</p>
   </div>
   <footer>
